public interface WritableSetMultimapValue<K,V> extends javafx.beans.value.WritableObjectValue<ObservableSetMultimap<K,V>>, ObservableSetMultimap<K,V>
A writable reference to an ObservableSetMultimap.

This interface provides identical functionality for SetMultimap as WritableMapValue for Map, WritableSetValue for Set, or WritableListValue for List.
